{"tid":856794,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"而家買iphone7會唔會好傻？","createTime":"2018-10-10T18:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T09:07:29.000Z","uid":51422,"like":10,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"c3e8c840a04acc43d3d4e570ac8446dc6b178a27","tid":856794,"uid":51422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T18:58:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我而家用緊嘅iphone se跌過幾次之後，唔知係咪右上粒制入面鬆左定點，而家會時不時跳去問你係咪關機嘅畫面。<br />\n<br />\n除左呢個問題同個芒裂左少少之外，部機係冇咩問題。但係成日會跳去關機畫面真係好煩，咁啱見到iphone7減左價。所以想問下大家轉iphone7平平地用住定去整番部好se<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b553d03eb8eef8e3c346b213f4115d34598ecd74","tid":856794,"uid":42991,"like":105,"dislike":9,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011b46cd77f2e8012b7e1a5f08545a6204a5fbc6","tid":856794,"uid":9658,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:12:33.000Z","msg":"唔使無線叉電同大mon的話，7手感好啲同輕好多<br />\n<br />\n之前用7而家用緊X，間中覺得後悔"},{"pid":"89924524a8e7052a2425ca70c8d107dd631e6297","tid":856794,"uid":123308,"like":8,"dislike":27,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:30:14.000Z","msg":"睇你自己清唔清楚自己想達成啲乜<br />\n<br />\n當年 iPhone 5 轉 5s，明知冇咁需要，<br />\n但因為 feel 到粒 sleep/wake button 就快打柴（iPhone 5 已知問題），<br />\n拿拿林襯仲用得 trade 走佢，再幫襯買 iPhone 5s<br />\n都係買返同 GB 數，因為我清楚知道自己目的只係襯 iPhone 5 仲有命盡快利用埋佢<br />\n<br />\n（點知買完冇耐，發覺我嗰批 iPhone 5 serial number / 年份後來都納入 replacement 之列，<br />\n變相我買 trade 走 5 嚟買 5s 呢個動作係多餘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呢個世界冇水晶球，<br />\n我當時只係做咗我應該做嘅嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-extends-iphone-5-sleepwake-button-replacement-program/）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnet.com%2Fnews%2Fapple-extends-iphone-5-sleepwake-button-replacement-program%2F%EF%BC%89&d=xflcCrgVt7Tsunh6gOrJRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=030ce97b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-extends-iphone-5-sleepwake-button-replacement-program/）</a><br />\n<br />\n所以睇樓主你清唔清楚自己做乜，清楚就去馬（只求用得，講求實際，唔追款）<br />\n分清 need 同 want 嘅分別"},{"pid":"2d70b9eba83506e25992730f0cbe7152d3258912","tid":856794,"uid":89514,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f64e0d751314a529d1a441838d5aa35d17e66d88","tid":856794,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:44:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6b8011d85967fd7e869e9067511916d5a0ea40e","tid":856794,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:48:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6597c1c7ac180c5d676aea47424806592717813","tid":856794,"uid":31361,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:51:35.000Z","msg":"我都煩緊<br />\n用來緊6仔細機 64g,<br />\n周不時爆位，上次去緊日本途中，<br />\n照到要簡相delete<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7+ 無左256，得128<br />\n<br />\n上8+又得256⋯<br />\n<br />\n2者差1600蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心大心細中"},{"pid":"cec8c57aae68a11d376d4541cb09812689c77333","tid":856794,"uid":15835,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:57:56.000Z","msg":"7 缺點係無 256<br />\n8 呀 XR 呀 嗰啲都無乜特別優點"},{"pid":"2e0ca0473c66d74b1c22370b528da259d48a0d1d","tid":856794,"uid":172778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T20:00:54.000Z","msg":"我都諗住買，用開唔想轉"},{"pid":"8c5614c56c5916dc3eeed882958f856590074026","tid":856794,"uid":1654,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T21:43:04.000Z","msg":"金屬背好正"},{"pid":"918ee95192258b2a3b418871303e372e35e4d4d9","tid":856794,"uid":29738,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T22:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f2d7f84c2709cf195f8c6c9bba1fa833c3f061","tid":856794,"uid":4285,"lik